<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<p><em>Ready in 10 minutes</em>, made from simple pantry staples, and packed with maximum flavorthis <strong>raw carrot salad</strong> is the ultimate quick lunch or side dish!</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-700x1050.jpg" alt="Top down view of a plate of raw carrot salad with a pair of chopsticks on a side." class="wp-image-24660" srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01640-scaled.jpg 1707w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure>



