Raw Carrot Salad">The Recipe:
Raw Carrot Salad</a></li></ul></nav><div class="toc-toggle-lt" onclick = "toggleViewMoreTOCLt(this)" aria-label="Expand table of contents"><button><span class="view-more">View more</span><span class="view-less" style="display:none">View less</span></button></div></div>
<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="why_youll_love_this_recipe"></span>Why You&#8217;ll Love This Recipe<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>It&#8217;s super quick</strong>! This raw carrot salad is ready in under 10 minutes, perfect for busy days.</li>



<li>The ribbons of carrot, crisp onion, and pistachios have the best crunchy texture in every bite.</li>



<li><strong>Naturally vibrant</strong> colors make it as visually appealing as it is tasty. Did you know that these colors also indicate the presence of phytonutrients that are good for you?</li>



<li><strong>If you love the combination of sweet and spicy</strong>, this recipe is for you! Maple syrup, chili flakes, and rice vinegar create a perfectly balanced flavor.</li>



<li>Making this raw carrot salad in a jar is not only <strong>meal prep friendly</strong>, it&#8217;s also easy to store and grab to go.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="key_ingredients"></span>Key Ingredients<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20700%201050'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-24662" data-lazy-srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-700x1050.png 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-300x450.png 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-768x1152.png 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-1024x1536.png 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-683x1024.png 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5.png 1200w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" data-lazy-src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-700x1050.png" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-700x1050.png" alt="" class="wp-image-24662" srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-700x1050.png 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-300x450.png 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-768x1152.png 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-1024x1536.png 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5-683x1024.png 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Plantyou-Labels-5.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript></figure>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Carrots</strong> are the star of the show. They are naturally sweet, crunchy, and bursting with color.</li>



<li><strong>Red onion</strong> adds sharpness and a slight bite to contrast the sweetness of the carrots.</li>



<li><strong>Cilantro</strong> brings a fresh, herbaceous note that lifts the entire salad.</li>



<li><strong>Sesame seeds and pistachios</strong> add a nutty crunch with a little healthy fat.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="hack_it"></span>Hack It!<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>For a <strong>nut-free option</strong>, swap pistachios for roasted sunflower seeds or pumpkin seeds.</li>



<li>You can only use toasted sesame seeds instead of sesame oil for an <strong>oil-free recipe</strong> version.</li>



<li>I think it&#8217;s delicious all on its own, but <strong>you can also serve it as a part of a bigger meal. </strong>Try it with rice and <a href="https://plantyou.com/honey-garlic-tofu/">&#8220;honey&#8221; garlic tofu</a> &#8211; yum!</li>



<li>Similarly, you can <strong>use this raw carrot salad in a sandwich or wrap. I</strong>t brightens the flavors and provides a splash of color!</li>



<li>Scale up in an instant for a larger portion or a big household.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="how_to_make_raw_carrot_salad"></span>How to Make Raw Carrot Salad<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">
<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20700%201050'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-24650" style="width:360px" data-lazy-srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-scaled.jpg 1707w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" data-lazy-src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-700x1050.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-700x1050.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-24650" style="width:360px" srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01624-scaled.jpg 1707w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript></figure>



<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Thinly slice onions and carrots (you can use a vegetable peeler for thin strips). Add the&nbsp;carrots, red onion and cilantro to a jar.</p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20700%201050'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-24651" style="width:360px" data-lazy-srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-scaled.jpg 1707w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" data-lazy-src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-700x1050.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-700x1050.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-24651" style="width:360px" srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01626-scaled.jpg 1707w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript></figure>



<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Throw in maple syrup, vinegar, chili flakes, sesame oil, sesame seeds and pistachios.&nbsp;</p>
</div>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">
<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20700%201050'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-24652" style="width:360px" data-lazy-srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-scaled.jpg 1707w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" data-lazy-src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-700x1050.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-700x1050.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-24652" style="width:360px" srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01627-scaled.jpg 1707w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript></figure>



<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Close the jar, and shake until completely mixed. Alternatively, mix everything together in a big salad bowl.</p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20700%201050'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-24657" style="width:360px" data-lazy-srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-scaled.jpg 1707w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" data-lazy-src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-700x1050.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="700" height="1050" src="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-700x1050.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-24657" style="width:360px" srcset="https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-300x450.jpg 300w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-1400x2100.jpg 1400w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://plantyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/DSC01636-scaled.jpg 1707w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript></figure>



<p><strong>Step 4</strong>: Enjoy immediately or let it marinate in the fridge for a few hours, It&#8217;s delicious either wapy!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div></div>



