<h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="the_recipe_raw_carrot_salad"></span><em>The Recipe:</em>
<span class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-normal">Raw Carrot Salad</span><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>

<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">Vibrant, deqlicious, and ready instantly! This salad is the perfect light lunch or side dish.</span></div>
