	<div class="caption">
	
					<h2>
									<em>hello &amp; welcome!</em>
							Hi, I'm Carleigh!			</h2>
				
		<p>You&#8217;ve made it to PlantYou where our mission is simple &#8211; to help you eat more plants. Peruse our recipes, meal planner and my cookbooks.</p>
		
